title: Concerned GOP push Rand Paul to focus on Senate re-election
text: > Top News Concerned GOP push Rand Paul to focus on Senate re-election FILE - In this July 23, 2015 file photo, Republican presidential candidate, Sen. Rand Paul, R-Ky., speaks on Capitol Hill in Washington. A defiant Rand Paul is brushing off weak fundraising and weaker poll numbers as some Republicans begin pushing him to abandon his presidential ambitions to focus on his Senate re-election. The first-term Kentucky senator this week claimed his superior political organization would prove wrong those doubting his chances in the White House contest. (AP Photo/Andrew Harnik, File)
